  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To demonstrate the value of multiple modalities and sustained clinically significant pain
      relief in patients with chronic pain when using the Boston Scientific Spectra WaveWriter
      Spinal Cord Stimulator (SCS) System.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
